title: Haven't received 10year gifts yet?
body: Title says it all, haven't gotten the icon or the kayle skin, and i've played several games before the release.

replies.body: We haven't finished sending out gifts, so hold tight and stay updated through our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-)!  You'll get the goods in time!
